---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// ABOUT — brand story & trust. Voice register: PRECISE / trust / brand-story.
// Positioning: Meridian is the most COMPLETE risk management for NinjaTrader 8 —
// a superset. Everything a traditional risk tool does, plus the behavioral layer
// none have. This page is who we are and why to trust us. Header, Footer and
// RiskBanner come from PageLayout. Text-forward; design system matches the
// homepage (light site, emerald accent, alternating bands, zinc cards).
//
// VENDOR CLAIM: the "Official NinjaTrader Ecosystem Vendor — audited and approved
// by NinjaTrader's Compliance, QA, and Executive teams" wording below is the
// owner-confirmed canonical claim (see CANONICAL-FACTS.md, VENDOR CLAIM section).
// Keep it in sync with that file; do not reintroduce the dropped-team or the
// fabricated "executive background check" variants that were removed.
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

const metadata = {
  title: 'About — Meridian',
  description:
    'Who Meridian is and why to trust it: the most complete risk management for NinjaTrader 8 — every limit a traditional risk tool has, plus the real-time behavioral layer none of them do. Built by traders. Official NinjaTrader Ecosystem Vendor. Local-first, anonymized, opt-out telemetry. No outcome guarantees.',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <!-- ───────────────────────── HERO ───────────────────────── -->
  <section class="halo">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 md:pt-24 pb-16 text-center" data-reveal>
      <p class="eyebrow text-[11px] font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-5">WHO WE ARE</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 leading-[1.06]">
        We built the most complete<br class="hidden md:block" /> risk tool for NinjaTrader 8.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-7 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg md:text-xl text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
        Everything a traditional risk tool gives you &mdash; daily loss limits, max size, P&amp;L and drawdown caps,
        loss-streak cutoffs &mdash; plus the one layer none of them have: real-time detection of the behavior that actually
        blows up accounts. We&rsquo;re a small team building exactly that, and nothing else.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ───────────────────────── WHY WE BUILT IT ───────────────────────── -->
  <section class="border-y border-zinc-200 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24" data-reveal>
      <p class="eyebrow text-[11px] font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">WHY MERIDIAN WAS BUILT</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">
        We built the tool we wished existed.
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-7 space-y-5 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Most trading software is built by engineers who have never traded, or by traders who outsource the
          engineering. Meridian sits at the intersection &mdash; built by traders who learned to ship software because
          no one else was going to build this.
        </p>
        <p>
          The frustration that started Meridian was simple: every existing risk tool fires <em>after</em> the damage. A
          daily loss limit trips at &minus;$500 &mdash; by then the revenge trade has already happened. A trade journal
          shows the pattern at 8pm &mdash; the next morning the same thing happens again.
        </p>
        <p>
          But the behavior that produces blown sessions is observable in real time. Re-entry pace shortens. Stops get
          widened. Sizing creeps up. Every one of these is measurable from the order stream NinjaTrader is already
          producing &mdash; no one had built the software to extract those signals and feed them back to the trader
          <em>during</em> the session.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900">So we did.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ───────────────────────── WHAT WE ARE — the superset ───────────────────────── -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-12" data-reveal>
      <p class="eyebrow text-[11px] font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">WHAT WE ARE</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">
        A superset, not a different tool.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
        Keep the safety net you already trust &mdash; Meridian has every part of it. Then it adds the behavioral layer
        no limit-based tool can reach: a live read on <em>how</em> you&rsquo;re trading, measured against your own
        baseline, that steps in before the order instead of after the loss.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 max-w-4xl" data-reveal>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-7">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-500 mb-4">Everything a traditional risk tool does</div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-zinc-700">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-zinc-400">&check;</span><span>Daily loss limit</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-zinc-400">&check;</span><span>Max position size</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-zinc-400">&check;</span><span>P&amp;L / drawdown caps</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-zinc-400">&check;</span><span>Loss-streak cutoff</span></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-5 text-sm text-zinc-500">Meridian does all of this too.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border-2 border-emerald-500 bg-emerald-50/40 p-7">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 mb-4">Plus the layer none of them have</div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-zinc-800">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold">&check;</span><span>Real-time detection of seven behavioral signals &mdash; revenge, oversizing, stop manipulation&hellip;</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold">&check;</span><span>A baseline that learns how <em>you</em> trade &mdash; not a generic average</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold">&check;</span><span>Intervention <em>before</em> the order, not after the loss</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold">&check;</span><span>The whole loop: monitor &middot; guard &middot; journal &middot; review</span></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-5 text-sm text-emerald-700 font-medium">No limit-based tool can do this.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-8 max-w-3xl text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
      We are not a trading guru. We do not sell signals, courses, mentorship, or Discord access. We are a small team
      building one thing &mdash; the most complete risk management for active discretionary futures traders on
      NinjaTrader 8. The Psychological Stability Index you&rsquo;ll see across the product is the mechanism, not the
      pitch: one live score, from seven measured signals, that tells you when discipline is slipping.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- ───────────────────────── OFFICIAL ECOSYSTEM VENDOR ───────────────────────── -->
  <!-- VENDOR CLAIM: the first paragraph below carries the owner-confirmed canonical
       vendor wording (see CANONICAL-FACTS.md, VENDOR CLAIM section). Keep it in sync
       with that file; do not reintroduce the deleted "executive background check" claim. -->
  <section class="border-y border-zinc-200 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24" data-reveal>
      <p class="eyebrow text-[11px] font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">OFFICIAL NINJATRADER ECOSYSTEM VENDOR</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">
        A standing we had to earn.
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-7 space-y-5 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Meridian is an <strong class="text-zinc-900">Official NinjaTrader Ecosystem Vendor</strong>. Our company, our
          website, our social channels, and the Meridian NT8 add-on itself were audited and approved by
          NinjaTrader&rsquo;s Compliance, QA, and Executive teams before being listed in the official Ecosystem.
        </p>
        <p>
          That review covered a signed Vendor Listing Agreement, a compliance audit of every public surface where we
          talk about trading, and a hands-on QA pass on the live NT8 add-on by NinjaTrader&rsquo;s internal QA team.
        </p>
        <p>
          Practically, that means two things for you. First, the product you install is the same product
          NinjaTrader&rsquo;s own team installed and tested. Second, the claims we make about Meridian have already
          cleared the retail-trading compliance bar NinjaTrader applies to every Ecosystem vendor &mdash; not just to us.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500">
          NinjaTrader&reg; is a registered trademark of NinjaTrader LLC. Meridian is operated by an independent company
          and is a third-party add-on for NinjaTrader 8; it is not owned by NinjaTrader LLC.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ───────────────────────── HONESTY STANCE ───────────────────────── -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-12" data-reveal>
      <p class="eyebrow text-[11px] font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">WHERE WE STAND</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">
        The promises &mdash; and the limits &mdash; in plain language.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
        A risk tool only earns trust if it&rsquo;s honest about its own boundaries. Here is exactly what Meridian does
        with your data, what it will and won&rsquo;t do, and what we will never claim.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5 max-w-5xl" data-reveal>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-7">
        <div class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-2">Anonymous by design</div>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
          Telemetry is local-first, anonymized, and opt-out. We never collect your name, broker credentials, account
          numbers, or funds. Anything used to improve the product or for research is tied to a random ID, never your
          identity, and is never sold. Opt out anytime.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-7">
        <div class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-2">Guard never closes unless you ask it to</div>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
          Guard enforces the rules you wrote when you were calm &mdash; by default it only blocks you from <em>adding</em>
          risk, never closing a live position on its own. The single exception is explicit and off by default: on a
          Trading Pause or Disconnect rule you <em>may</em> opt in to auto-flatten open positions when it fires. You can always exit, any time.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-7">
        <div class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-2">No outcome guarantees</div>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
          We don&rsquo;t publish track records, account statements, or &ldquo;I made $X&rdquo; screenshots, and we never
          promise profits. Meridian improves self-awareness and discipline; outcomes still depend on many factors beyond
          psychology.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ───────────────────────── HOW WE OPERATE ───────────────────────── -->
  <section class="border-y border-zinc-200 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24" data-reveal>
      <p class="eyebrow text-[11px] font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">HOW WE OPERATE</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900">
        Small team. Public roadmap. Direct support.
      </h2>
      <ul class="mt-7 space-y-4 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed list-disc pl-5 marker:text-emerald-600">
        <li>Two tiers: <strong class="text-zinc-900">Core at $49.99/mo</strong> and <strong class="text-zinc-900">Guard at $69.99/mo</strong>, both with a 7-day free trial. Sold via Whop; cancel anytime.</li>
        <li>Updates ship publicly through the <a href="/download" class="text-emerald-700 underline hover:text-emerald-900">changelog</a> &mdash; you can see exactly what changed and when.</li>
        <li>Support goes to <a href="mailto:contactmeridianpsi@gmail.com" class="text-emerald-700 underline hover:text-emerald-900">contactmeridianpsi@gmail.com</a> and is answered within 24 hours. We read every email.</li>
        <li>The team is small on purpose. Every change to the product is reviewed by someone who understands both the trading workflow and the code.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-7 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
        If you have feedback, a bug report, or a feature request &mdash; send it. The roadmap is shaped by traders who
        actually use the tool.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ───────────────────────── PSI SCOPE — behavioral proxy ───────────────────────── -->
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">
      PSI is a behavioral proxy index derived from your trading activity inside NinjaTrader. It does not measure
      physiology (for example heart rate or stress hormones), and it is not validated as a predictor of trading profits
      or losses. Meridian is designed to improve self-awareness and discipline during a session; outcomes still depend on
      many factors beyond psychology.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- ───────────────────────── FINAL CTA ───────────────────────── -->
  <section class="halo">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 text-center" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 leading-[1.06]">
        Trade the version of you<br class="hidden md:block" /> that you respect.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-zinc-600">
        Everything your risk tool does &mdash; plus the part that actually saves the account.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-9">
        <a href="/pricing" class="inline-block font-semibold text-white bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg transition shadow-sm">Start your 7-day free trial</a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-zinc-500">No charge until day 7 &middot; From $49.99/mo &middot; NinjaTrader 8 required</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
